description:
Minecraft Server. Did Bdubs sneak the end rod back? Today we check out the "What is Love?" note block song we installed at Keralis' base. Then it's time to head to the Nether to start up our Nether farming at a new base location. First off, we setup a couple simple Blaze farms.

Note Block Music: 
Modest Mouse - Float On
RuneScape - Sea Shanty 2
Haddaway - What is Love?
Super Metroid - Lower Norfair
Cave Story - Jenka 1
